Samsung Core Prime Modification Instructions:

The first step is to root your phone. If you are on GitHub looking at this device you probably know the consequences of rooting,
but for the less educated, it may break your phone. It will never destroy it completely, but you will get scared and maybe panic 
(seriously this phone is like $25. chill...). But don't. All you have to do is flash the ROM in the link again and everything
should be brand new again.

To root, first you should probably backup your phone first. To backup before rooting, please refer to this link:
http://www.iroot.com/knowledge-tips/how-to-backup-android-before-rooting.html 

To root, install the KingRoot.apk onto your phone, and run it. 
